        <section>
            <h2>General OER Platforms</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="https://www.oercommons.org" target="_blank">OER Commons</a> - A comprehensive library of open educational resources.</li>
                <li><a href="https://openstax.org" target="_blank">OpenStax</a> - Free, peer-reviewed, openly licensed textbooks in various subjects.</li>
                <li><a href="https://www.merlot.org" target="_blank">MERLOT</a> - A curated collection of free learning and teaching materials.</li>
                <li><a href="https://www.saylor.org" target="_blank">Saylor Academy</a> - Free, self-paced courses in a variety of disciplines.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>Science & Mathematics</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="https://www.ck12.org/student/" target="_blank">CK-12</a> - Free resources for math, science, and more, for K-12 students.</li>
                <li><a href="https://ocw.mit.edu/index.htm" target="_blank">MIT OpenCourseWare</a> - Free access to MIT's course materials on science, engineering, and math.</li>
                <li><a href="https://phet.colorado.edu" target="_blank">PhET Interactive Simulations</a> - Free science and math simulations from the University of Colorado Boulder.</li>
                <li><a href="https://www.khanacademy.org" target="_blank">Khan Academy</a> - A vast library of free instructional videos and exercises in math and science.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>Humanities & Social Sciences</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="https://open.umn.edu/opentextbooks" target="_blank">Open Textbook Library</a> - Free and openly licensed textbooks on subjects such as history, sociology, and philosophy.</li>
                <li><a href="https://www.oerproject.com" target="_blank">OER Project</a> - Free history projects and lessons, including Big History and World History Project.</li>
                <li><a href="https://online.stanford.edu/courses" target="_blank">Stanford Online</a> - Free courses in literature, history, and social sciences from Stanford University.</li>
                <li><a href="https://courses.lumenlearning.com/catalog/humanities" target="_blank">Lumen Learning</a> - Free courses in arts and humanities, designed for higher education.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>Languages & Literature</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="https://www.languageguide.org" target="_blank">LanguageGuide</a> - Free audio and visual vocabulary guides for a variety of languages.</li>
                <li><a href="https://libretexts.org" target="_blank">LibreTexts</a> - Open textbooks on language, literature, and communication studies.</li>
                <li><a href="https://www.oercommons.org/hubs/world-languages" target="_blank">OER Commons: World Languages</a> - Free learning resources for language studies.</li>
                <li><a href="https://opentextbc.ca" target="_blank">BCcampus OpenEd</a> - A collection of open textbooks, including language and literature subjects.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>Business & Economics</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="https://www.saylor.org/majors/business-administration/" target="_blank">Saylor Academy: Business</a> - Free courses in business administration and management.</li>
                <li><a href="https://ocw.mit.edu/courses/sloan-school-of-management/" target="_blank">MIT OCW: Business & Management</a> - Free course materials from MIT’s Sloan School of Management.</li>
                <li><a href="https://open.umn.edu/opentextbooks/subjects/business" target="_blank">Open Textbook Library: Business</a> - Free textbooks in business and economics.</li>
                <li><a href="https://www.khanacademy.org/economics-finance-domain" target="_blank">Khan Academy: Economics & Finance</a> - Free lessons on economics and personal finance.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>
